io\/ratio","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ratio"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Double"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/ratio"},"https://accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr":{"type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","url":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","title":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Contains a set of helpers and extensions shared for higher level targets."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"Foundations","images":[{"identifier":"ic_layers.png","type":"icon"}]},"ic_layers.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSFoundations\/ic_layers.png"}],"alt":null,"type":"image","identifier":"ic_layers.png"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","abstract":[{"text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is for example the case for France with the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"also named “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"kind":"symbol"}}}